data: Oliviero Andreussi, Ph.D. Oliviero Andreussi, Ph.D. Assistant Professor 940-369-5316 Oliviero.Andreussi@unt.edu Physics Building 318 https://sites.google.com/site/olivieroandreussi/home https://facultyinfo.unt.edu/faculty-profile?query=Oliviero+Andreussi&type=name&profile=oa0146 I am a researcher working in the fields of Computational Chemistry and Materials Science.
